243
00:13:52.291 --> 00:13:53.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Am I all right?</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:13:54.291 --> 00:13:58.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No magic, no science</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or Goddess can cure me.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:13:58.208 --> 00:14:03.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A cure requires making me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>other than who I was, who I still am.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:14:03.333 --> 00:14:07.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This disease is a part of me.</c.bg_transparent>
