247
00:14:08.041 --> 00:14:09.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I will die, Papa.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:14:09.833 --> 00:14:13.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No one can change that.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Not even you can change that.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:14:17.125 --> 00:14:19.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Invoker] Filomena. I know.</c.bg_transparent>

