00:14:20.791 --> 00:14:22.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've always known.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:14:23.250 --> 00:14:24.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought…</c.bg_transparent>

