267
00:15:23.583 --> 00:15:24.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Brave.</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:15:24.791 --> 00:15:26.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Mirana] And very human.</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:15:29.833 --> 00:15:33.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When you were small,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you begged me for a dollhouse.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:15:33.958 --> 00:15:37.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I failed to see the need,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but I could refuse you nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:15:38.208 --> 00:15:40.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Invoker] </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>So I conjured a structure
based on the Palace of Hurra'agdu.</i></c.bg_transparent>

272
00:15:41.041 --> 00:15:43.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>It was accurate to the last detail.</i></c.bg_transparent>

273
00:15:44.083 --> 00:15:45.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I remember.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:15:45.333 --> 00:15:47.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And I remember bursting into tears.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:15:47.333 --> 00:15:49.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Happy tears, I believed.</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:15:49.666 --> 00:15:53.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Invoker] </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Until you demanded
