277
00:15:53.333 --> 00:15:57.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wanted a dollhouse as I imagined it,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>not as you imagined it.</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:15:57.875 --> 00:15:58.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Invoker] Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:15:59.000 --> 00:16:02.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So we commissioned the greatest artisan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the Nightsilver Woods</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:16:02.541 --> 00:16:04.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to build a new one.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:16:04.125 --> 00:16:06.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Invoker] </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>You sat with him,
