283
00:16:11.791 --> 00:16:14.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's beautiful. I still have it.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:16:15.375 --> 00:16:17.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Filomena] Nothing is beyond repair.</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:16:18.708 --> 00:16:20.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Papa, I was thinking.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:16:20.791 --> 00:16:22.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps there is another way.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:16:23.500 --> 00:16:24.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A better way.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:16:28.291 --> 00:16:31.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are the Eye.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Literally the sun over our heads.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:16:31.666 --> 00:16:34.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A constant in the universe,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>linked to all stars,</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:16:34.833 --> 00:16:36.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>linked to all universes.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:16:36.750 --> 00:16:39.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Filomena] </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>You remember
