292
00:16:39.166 --> 00:16:42.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>and your divine spark connects you
to the Pillars of Creation.</i></c.bg_transparent>

293
00:16:43.083 --> 00:16:45.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Eye carries innate knowledge</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:16:45.166 --> 00:16:49.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>of things my father took</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>thousands of iterations to learn.</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:16:49.291 --> 00:16:52.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Kashurra] </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Across 15 planes
and countless realities,</i></c.bg_transparent>

296
00:16:52.875 --> 00:16:54.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I found one constant.</i></c.bg_transparent>

297
00:16:54.833 --> 00:16:57.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>The sun in the sky. The Worldwyrm.</i></c.bg_transparent>

298
00:16:58.958 --> 00:17:02.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You want me to restore</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the reality I came from.</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:17:02.625 --> 00:17:04.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Filomena] I don't want any of this.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:17:04.208 --> 00:17:08.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you can put it all back as it was,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as you knew it.</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:17:12.416 --> 00:17:13.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know what I'm asking.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:17:14.666 --> 00:17:21.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're asking me to save what I love</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by allowing what I've loved to die.</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:17:23.625 --> 00:17:26.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Luna, Marci, all of you.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:17:27.541 --> 00:17:30.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish I knew how to say goodbye again.</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:17:31.708 --> 00:17:34.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yet my confusion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is in some ways a blessing…</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:17:35.708 --> 00:17:39.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because it means I was privileged</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to have you in my life.</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:17:40.458 --> 00:17:41.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I will not forget you.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:17:42.833 --> 00:17:43.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I love you.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:17:48.083 --> 00:17:52.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are the best parts of me</c.bg_transparent>
