311
00:17:57.666 --> 00:17:58.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There always is.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:18:03.583 --> 00:18:06.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[intense music]</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:18:07.083 --> 00:18:08.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reach out with your mind.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:18:10.125 --> 00:18:12.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ignore the illusion of the physical world.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:18:18.083 --> 00:18:20.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Invoker] </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>See the Pillars
