316
00:18:35.083 --> 00:18:36.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Draw them to you.</i></c.bg_transparent>

317
00:18:38.041 --> 00:18:40.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[mystic music]</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:18:56.625 --> 00:18:57.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wait.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:19:00.833 --> 00:19:03.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mirana, no. It's okay, I'm okay.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:19:05.041 --> 00:19:08.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I used to think my name</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was the most important thing in the world.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:19:08.791 --> 00:19:12.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now I know it's how I'm remembered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that matters, and who remembers me.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:19:13.041 --> 00:19:17.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Even if this works,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the last thing I'll see is you.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:19:17.916 --> 00:19:21.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll watch you die</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>knowing I was the cause.</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:19:21.708 --> 00:19:23.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not the cause.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:19:23.833 --> 00:19:26.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can let you go, him go.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:19:27.833 --> 00:19:30.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know that I can kill you.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:19:31.500 --> 00:19:33.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Davion] This is my choice.</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:19:34.583 --> 00:19:35.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What I want.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:19:40.708 --> 00:19:43.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[sucks teeth]</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know, most men would say the opposite.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:19:44.333 --> 00:19:45.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not most men.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:19:47.666 --> 00:19:50.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come here. Come to me on your own.</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:19:50.250 --> 00:19:51.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll do this together.</c.bg_transparent>

